speech: If lucky be not proud , if unlucky do not depressed by the loss of hope.
There is no lucky or unlucky according to me,  if you really work hard then you surely achieve the success , you have to wait for the moment.
Be with patience . Sometimes you have to go through the worst to get the best.
Don't be prisoner of the past , be the architect of the future.
Don't depend on luck, depend on hard work .
You are the author for your next chapter.
If you don't struggle, you don't improve.
Learn to fight alone.
Never explain yourself to anyone.The person who likes you doesn't need it.The person who dislikes you won't believe it.
Today's generation logic: Low pitch of voice is always considered "FAKE". Shout out load,lose temper and only then , you'll be considered "REAL".
Fears can be controlled, but tears never lie.
"The Sun watches what i do, but the Moon knows all my secrets."
Don't sacrifice your time for people who wouldn't do the same for you.
Sometimes you need to stand alone to stand out.
Don't quit . You are already in pain. You're already hurt. Get a reward from it.
Don't think too much! just do what makes you happy!
May your haters live long to see your success!
"I really hate when i'm in good mood and suddenly bad happens and ruins everything."
"If you have been hurt many times and you still know how to smile , trust me you are "Damn" strong."
"I don't respect those who don't respect me. You may call it selfish but i call it self respect."
Never beg anyone , Never trust anyone, Never depend on anyone.
